The shittiest irssi plugin ever. Automagical emoji tags
Because we all <3 Knifa on #glasnost.
----------------------------------------------------------

Instructions:

1) put script in ~/.irssi/scripts
2) put .db file in ~/.irssi/
3) /script load emojis.pl
4) Use /emojis to display the list
5) Marvel at your ability to use things like :table:

You may add your own to the database, format is:

  :trigger:
  smiley

Your trigger MUST begin with ':'.

NOTE: there is also a weechat version now: https://github.com/mrdaemon/weechat-emojis


